{"tid":108840,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[西藏] 阿里南線 + 西寧火車","createTime":"2017-02-05T14:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T02:56:52.000Z","uid":15965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21f76b4fc5ab15ef17fa0d804d94253a42ca1d6e","tid":108840,"uid":15965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"有無巴打行過阿里南線？<br />\n我上網搵到呢個行程：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2248eD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2248eD.jpg&h=ccd7e33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我地可能得十三日，有無邊日可以Cut ？<br />\n<br />\n另外有無巴打試過係西寧坐火車入拉薩可以分享下？"},{"pid":"771a10cbcc48f636dd51704aafc90e1601120bfe","tid":108840,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"預鬆好過緊<br />\n<br />\n高反，去到同行有人高反，都打亂你安排。<br />\n壞車<br />\n天氣，上到珠峰天氣唔好，睇唔到珠峰，你住定唔住多晚丫？<br />\n<br />\n全部都唔到你控制"},{"pid":"db8f9290dca1462fa75abbd42af48b006891d5ec","tid":108840,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"路線大致上一樣 但我地無去珠峰 係崗仁波齊果面留左兩日轉山 回程去拉薩時兜埋去納木錯留一晚  加埋都係10日"},{"pid":"5cbc06334e5753644100a42105b59b2d2092ee1f","tid":108840,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預鬆好過緊<br />\n<br />\n高反，去到同行有人高反，都打亂你安排。<br />\n壞車<br />\n天氣，上到珠峰天氣唔好，睇唔到珠峰，你住定唔住多晚丫？<br />\n<br />\n全部都唔到你控制</blockquote><br />\n同意 到時你唔知會遇上啲咩  凈係高反都可以好大變數"},{"pid":"13762493b8e30947a0129ac2a965a33c76382865","tid":108840,"uid":49952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"可以去轉山？ 之前去，話香港人唔可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0729ed67999086b965ea27727b9eb0b174470ca","tid":108840,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去轉山？ 之前去，話香港人唔可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉完未